<HEADLINE>
FT  10 SEP 93 / Review to focus on funding of industry
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A review focusing on whether business has access to the funds it needs was
announced by Mr Kenneth Clarke, the chancellor, last night.
The review will examine the role of financial institutions in funding
industry, in particular small businesses. Report, Page 20
</TEXT>
