FT  09 SEP 93 / International Company News: HK and China Gas 19% ahead
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By SIMON DAVIES
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   HONG KONG
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
HONG KONG and China Gas, Hong Kong's monopoly gas supplier controlled by the
Lee family's Henderson Investment, has increased first-half net profit 19
per cent to HKDollars 560.2m (USDollars 72.7m) up from Dollars HK472.2m in
1992.
Turnover was HKDollars 1.68bn, up from HKDollars 1.53bn, due to a steady
